embedding-and-chunking-24","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking#6-落地建议","content":"每次只改一个变量（切块大小、重叠、检索 k、重排模型）；"},"177":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking-25","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking#6-落地建议","content":"记录“检索结果 + 最终回答”，定位问题在检索还是生成；"},"178":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking-26","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/embedding-and-chunking#6-落地建议","content":"设立回归阈值，避免优化 A 场景却破坏 B 场景。"},"179":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations","type":"page","content":"Introduction","breadcrumbs":["Docs","Introduction","AI Engineering","Foundations"],"tags":[],"url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations"},"180":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations-0","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations","content":"模型、上下文、RAG、Embedding 等基础原理"},"181":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations-1","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations#本模块覆盖的核心问题","content":"本模块覆盖的核心问题"},"182":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations-2","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations#关键设计原则","content":"关键设计原则"},"183":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations-3","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations#常见反模式","content":"常见反模式"},"184":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations-4","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations","content":"这一部分回答“为什么这样做”，用于建立 A