/docs/ai-engineering/foundations","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations#常见反模式","content":"只追求通过率，不治理长尾错误与失败类型分布。"},"195":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window","type":"page","content":"Context Window 设计","breadcrumbs":["Docs","Introduction","AI Engineering","Foundations"],"tags":[],"url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window"},"196":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window-0","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window","content":"在 Context Window 限制内设计 Prompt 与 Task Slice 的方法。"},"197":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window-1","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window#1-问题定义context-window-不是容量而是约束系统","content":"1) 问题定义：Context Window 不是“容量”，而是“约束系统”"},"198":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window-2","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window#2-设计目标把-token-当预算来管理","content":"2) 设计目标：把 token 当预算来管理"},"199":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window-3","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window#3-实践策略","content":"3) 实践策略"},"200":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window-4","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window#指令分层","content":"指令分层"},"201":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window-5","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window#历史管理","content":"历史管理"},"202":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window-6","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window#预算配比可作为初始模板","content":"预算配比（可作为初始模板）"},"203":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window-7","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window#4-失败模式与修复","content":"4) 失败模式与修复"},"204":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window-8","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window#5-落地检查清单","content":"5) 落地检查清单"},"205":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window-9","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window#1-问题定义context-window-不是容量而是约束系统","content":"Context Window 不只是 token 上限，更是指令优先级、注意力分配和成本结构的综合约束。超限不是唯一问题，常见情况是“未超限但质量退化”，例如指令被稀释、关键信息埋在中段（lost-in-the-middle）。"},"206":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window-10","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window#2-设计目标把-token-当预算来管理","content":"保留“不可丢信息”：系统指令、任务目标、强约束条件；"},"207":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window-11","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window#2-设计目标把-token-当预算来管理","content":"控制“高变信息”：用户上下文、检索片段、临时中间结果；"},"208":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window-12","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window#2-设计目标把-token-当预算来管理","content":"压缩“低价值信息”：冗余对话历史、重复日志、无效失败尝试。"},"209":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window-13","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window#指令分层","content":"系统层：角色、边界、输出格式、禁止项；"},"210":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window-14","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window#指令分层","content":"任务层：当前目标、输入摘要、验收标准；"},"211":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window-15","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window#指令分层","content":"证据层：检索结果、日志片段、结构化数据。"},"212":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window-16","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window#历史管理","content":"对话历史采用“滚动摘要 + 关键锚点”而非全文回放；"},"213":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window-17","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window#历史管理","content":"对失败尝试只保留“失败原因 + 不可行路径”，减少重复踩坑；"},"214":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window-18","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window#历史管理","content":"明确历史有效期，过期信息进入归档，不再默认注入。"},"215":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window-19","page_id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/model-context-window#预算配比可作为初始模板","content":"15%：系统与约束；"},"216":{"id":"/docs/ai-engineering/foundations/mod